                                <div t-attf-id="collapse#{toll.id}" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                        <t t-foreach="toll.toll_ids" t-as="tl">
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                                    <t t-esc="tl.name"/>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-3">
                                                    <t t-esc="tl.type"/>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-3">
                                                    <t class="decimal_precision"
                                                       t-att-data-precision="str(tl.currency_id.decimal_places)">
                                                        <span t-esc="tl.amount"
                                                              t-options='{"widget":"monetary", "display_currency" : tl.currency_id,}'/>
                                                    </t>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </t>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </t>
                </div>
            </div>
        </t>
    </template>
    <!--FAQs page design-->
    <template id='FAQs_page' name="FAQs">
        <t t-call="website.layout">
            <input type="hidden" t-att-value="request.env.uid" id="uid"/>
            <h1>
                <center>Frequently Asked Questions</center>
            </h1>
            <div class="container" id="FAQsDiv" style="margin-top:8% !important;">
                <!--question 1-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>What is ETC?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse1" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                ETC is a program for Electronic Toll Collection on Toll Plazas on Highways.
                                ETC employs Radio Frequency Identification (RFID) technology for
                                making toll payments directly from the prepaid account linked to it.
                                It is affixed on the windscreen of your vehicle and enables you to drive
                                through toll plazas
                                ETC offers near non-stop movement of vehicles through toll plazas
                                and the convenience of cashless payment of toll fee with nation-wide
                                interoperable Electronic Toll Collection Services.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <!--question 2-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>Is ETC compulsory and is ETC for any particular kind/category of vehicle?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse2" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">No, ETC is not compulsory.
                                It is voluntary at this stage of the program.
                                However, it may be made mandatory in future at some locations.
                                ETC is applicable for all categories, kinds, makes and types of vehicles.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--question 3-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>How will I get to know if and how much toll has been debited?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse3" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                The customer will receive an SMS with requisite details to his registered mobile number
                                as soon as the toll transaction takes place.
                                Periodic statement of account may also be obtained on website of the
                                Issuer Agency after registration by the customer.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--question 4-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>How and where do I finally pay the toll?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse4" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                Issuer Agency will electronically deduct the applicable toll fee from the customer’s
                                account linked to the ETC.
                                This deduction will be done post the toll transaction.
                                The customer needs to adequately fund the account which is linked to ETC.
                                This recharge process may be termed as top-up.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--question 5-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>Can one vehicle use more than one ETC?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse5" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                It is strictly prohibited to purchase
                                two ETC for one vehicle. In case of multiple ETC,
                                customer will be responsible for operational issues.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--question 6-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>How would I cross toll plaza, if ETC equipment are not working?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse4" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                In case ETC equipment are not working and your ETC account is having sufficient balance,
                                please pay the toll fee in cash at the plaza. Additionally, please call our customer
                                care
                                and also
                                report the issue with the concessionaire.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!--question 7-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>How can I buy RFID Tag and what documents and recharge are required?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse4" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                Customer need to submit a copy of the following documents along with the application for
                                RFID Tag:
                                1.Registration Certificate (RC) of the vehicle.
                                2.Passport size photograph of the vehicle owner
                                3.KYC documents as per the category of the vehicle owner (viz. individual /
                                corporate):Individual

                                ID proof and Address proof from the list mentioned, and 1 passport size photograph
                                1.Driving License,
                                2.PAN Card Passport,
                                3.Voter ID Card,
                                4.Aadhar Card (with address)
                                <b>For instance, valid driving license would be sufficient for Address and ID proof.</b>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!--question 8-->
                <div class="panel-group">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div>What are the benefits of using RFID Tag?</div>
                                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse4" style="float:right;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-caret-down" style="position: relative;top: -18px;"/>
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                1.Ease of payment – No need to carry cash for the toll transactions, saves time
                                2.Near non-stop movement of vehicles leading to lower fuel cost.
                                3.Reduced toll payment hassles
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    Note:
                    <ol type="I">
                        <li>Issue of RFID Tag is subject to verification of original documents mentioned above by the
                            issuing
                            agency.
                        </li>
                        <li>Customers are advised to bring originals of above documents while visiting PoS for purchase
                            of
                            Tag.
                        </li>
                        <li>The RFIDTag will be fixed on the vehicle’s windshield by the representative of the Issuer
                            Agency only.
                        </li>

                        <li>Any representative of the vehicle owner can provide the above documentation and information
                            and
                            purchase the Tag.
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </t>
    </template>

    <!--Feedback Page design-->
    <template id='feedback_page' name="Feedback">
        <t t-call="website.layout">
            <input type="hidden" t-att-value="request.env.uid" id="uid"/>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="container">
                    <form method="POST" action="/feedback">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <h2>Feedback</h2>
                            <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" t-att-value="request.csrf_token()"/>
                            <textarea class="form-control" rows="10" id="comment" name="comment"
                                      placeholder="Enter your feedback.."/>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info" style="margin-top:10px;">Add Feedback</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="container">
                    <t t-set="feedbacks" t-value="request.env['toll.feedback'].sudo().search([])"/>
                    <div class="commentBox">
                        <div class="actionBox">
                            <ul class="commentList">
                                <t t-foreach="feedbacks" t-as="feedback">
                                    <li>
                                        <div class="commenterImage">
                                            <img t-att-src="'/web/image?model=res.users&amp;field=image&amp;id='+str(feedback.user_id.id)"/>
                                        </div>
                                        <t t-if="feedback.user_id.id == request.env.user.id">
                                            <a class="remove_feedback" t-attf-id="#{feedback.id}">
                                                <span style="float:right !important;font-size:18px;">
                                                    <i class="fa fa-trash"/>
                                                </span>
                                            </a>
                                        </t>
                                        <div class="commentText">
                                            <p>
                                                <b>
                                                    <span t-esc="feedback.user_id.name"/>
                                                </b>
                                            </p>
                                            <p>
                                                <span t-esc="feedback.feedback"/>
                                            </p>
                                            <span class="date sub-text">
                                                <span t-esc="feedback.create_date"/>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                    </li>
                                </t>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </t>
    </template>

    <template id='scan_page' name="Scan">
        <t t-call="website.layout">
            <div>
                <input type="hidden" t-att-value="request.env.uid" id="uid"/>
                <form class="oe_signup_form" role="form" method="post" t-if="not message">
                    <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" t-att-value="request.csrf_token()"/>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="fname" class="control-label">First Name *</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" t-att-value="fname" id="fname" class="form-control"
                               required="required" t-att-readonly="'readonly' if only_passwords else None"
                        />
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </t>
    </template>

